Emma: Is this... a flute...? An ocarina...?  #line:ch3_p2_FairyForest_3

Frecia: Yes. If you play this magic ocarina while picturing in your mind where you want to go, the wind will carry you through the sky and you will arrive at that destination.  #line:ch3_p2_FairyForest_4
Frecia:  However, since it must be a place that you can picture in your mind, it has to be a place that you have visited before.  #line:ch3_p2_FairyForest_5

Emma: Still, wow... This would make our journey a lot easier to navigate!  #line:ch3_p2_FairyForest_6
