Emma: But I didn't know there was such a thing that existed in the Fairy Forest.  #line:ch3_p2_FairyForest_7

Frecia: Hmmm... it's okay Emma, it's not just you, it's something I've kept from everyone else. This is so precious that if the prank-loving fairies knew about it, they would get themselves in big trouble, wouldn't you think? Very few people know that this ocarina exists.  #line:ch3_p2_FairyForest_8

Emma: Oh, that's how it was. I'm glad I'm not the only one who didn't know…  #line:ch3_p2_FairyForest_9

Bravo: That's right, that's right! If those guys mess with a whistle like that, it's not going to be good! After all, my Hero was tricked into the pit by those munchkins!"  #line:ch3_p2_FairyForest_10

Frecia: Oh dear... in the pit...? Umm...sorry about that. But it was a cute prank that didn't take your life, right? You see, fairies are fun and mischievous, eternal and frail, free in their small world, very naughty but at the same time very cute. They are all my darlings.  #line:ch3_p2_FairyForest_11

Bravo: Oh really! I don’t think they are cute at all!  #line:ch3_p2_FairyForest_12

Emma: Bravo enough already! Please address Lady Frecia with some manners!  #line:ch3_p2_FairyForest_13

Bravo: By the way, can my hero play that flute? I know it's a strange shape, but does it really make any sound?  #line:ch3_p2_FairyForest_14
