Emma: It's not a funny shape, it's an actual instrument called an ocarina.  #line:ch3_p2_FairyForest_15
Emma:Bravo, you may not know this, but this boy is a runner-up in the Tron Village Ocarina Endurance Performance Festival!  #line:ch3_p2_FairyForest_16

Bravo: Ocarina International Festival...?  #line:ch3_p2_FairyForest_17
