title: ch3_e4_FairyForest_1_5
tags:
---
Emma: Yes, yes! Our village has all kinds of festivals! Because we are in the countryside and everyone is bored! We also have a log sawing festival, a poor pumpkin throwing festival, a see how far you can pile up the stones festival, and many others…  #line:ch3_p2_FairyForest_18

Frecia: Hmmm... it sounds fun and intriguing, but we'll talk about the festivals later.  #line:ch3_p2_FairyForest_19

Emma: Ah! Excuse me, Lady Frecia!  #line:ch3_p2_FairyForest_20

Frecia: Earlier I have said that you may stay until you have defeated the demons around the Fairy Forest….However, I will allow you special access to this Fairy Forest for the time being until you have defeated the Demon King. But only to the extent of the loopholes and pathways you are using now."  #line:ch3_p2_FairyForest_21

Emma: Lady Frecia, Are you sure about this?!  #line:ch3_p2_FairyForest_22

Frecia: Yes, in recognition of your skills. In return, I want you to lend me your ear, if the other fairies and I have any problems. Our problems are resolved for now, but the threat from demons hasn't completely disappeared."  #line:ch3_p2_FairyForest_23

Emma: That's of course... that's fine with you... right?  #line:ch3_p2_FairyForest_24
===
title: ch3_e4_FairyForest_1_6
tags:
